#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn20.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga "
msgstr "1. Similes "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Sattisutta "
msgstr "5. A Spear "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.265, sc1
msgctxt "sn20.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.5:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, satti tiṇhaphalā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose there was a sharp-pointed spear. "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.3"
msgid "Atha puriso āgaccheyya: "
msgstr "And a man came along and thought, "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.4"
msgid "‘ahaṃ imaṃ sattiṃ tiṇhaphalaṃ pāṇinā vā muṭṭhinā vā paṭileṇissāmi paṭikoṭṭissāmi paṭivaṭṭessāmī’ti. "
msgstr "‘With my hand or fist I’ll fold this sharp spear over, bend it back, and twist it around!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.5:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.6"
msgid "bhabbo nu kho so puriso amuṃ sattiṃ tiṇhaphalaṃ pāṇinā vā muṭṭhinā vā paṭileṇetuṃ paṭikoṭṭetuṃ paṭivaṭṭetun”ti? "
msgstr "Is that man capable of doing so?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.5:1.7"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir. "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.8"
msgid "“Taṃ kissa hetu”? "
msgstr "Why not? "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.9"
msgid "“Asu hi, bhante, satti tiṇhaphalā na sukarā pāṇinā vā muṭṭhinā vā paṭileṇetuṃ paṭikoṭṭetuṃ paṭivaṭṭetuṃ. "
msgstr "Because it’s not easy to fold that sharp spear over, bend it back, and twist it around with the hand or fist. "

msgctxt "sn20.5:1.10"
msgid "Yāvadeva ca pana so puriso kilamathassa vighātassa bhāgī assā”ti. "
msgstr "That man will eventually get weary and frustrated.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn20.5:2.1"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, yassa kassaci bhikkhuno mettācetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā, tassa ce amanusso cittaṃ khipitabbaṃ maññeyya; "
msgstr "“In the same way, suppose a mendicant has developed the heart’s release by love, has cultivated it, made it a vehicle and a basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly implemented it. Should any non-human think to overthrow their mind, "

msgctxt "sn20.5:2.2"
msgid "atha kho sveva amanusso kilamathassa vighātassa bhāgī assa. "
msgstr "they’ll eventually get weary and frustrated. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.5:2.3"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "sn20.5:2.4"
msgid "‘mettā no cetovimutti bhāvitā bhavissati bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will develop the heart’s release by love. We’ll cultivate it, make it our vehicle and our basis, keep it up, consolidate it, and properly implement it.’ "

msgctxt "sn20.5:2.5"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.5:2.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

